{"tid":2515421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：緬甸中部有包裹爆炸　4人死亡包括3名警員","createTime":"2021-05-04T03:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T03:52:51.000Z","uid":290404,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0ab0de3fed3e77ec00489d64bba8783952ab4f","tid":2515421,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:35:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緬甸發生軍事政變至今超過3個月，反對軍方的示威仍然持續。路透社報道，中部勃固省昨日下午至少發生一宗包裹炸彈爆炸事件，造成5人死亡，包括<strong>3名警員</strong>、一名全國民主同盟地區議員及一名平民。另外有一名警員嚴重受傷。<br />\n<br />\n位於北部的克欽族民族武裝組織表示，<strong>在近日持續與軍方發生衝突期間，擊落一架軍方直升機。</strong>另外，當地傳媒報道，<strong>一名由軍方任命的行政人員被人用刀刺死</strong>，暫時未知行兇者身份。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述總部設在緬甸的一個監察團體表示，政變發生以來，有至少766名示威者死亡。報道又引述軍方說，<strong>至少24名保安部隊人員被殺</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589112-20210504.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589112-20210504.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnsjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=b46d95f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589112-20210504.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5a06c4a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589112-20210504.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"68a1e754cf766c9d2c22dcdb94be5d871a1e2462","tid":2515421,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:49:05.000Z","msg":"同得3個popo一齊<br />\n個議員同平民都係藍架啦"},{"pid":"2a6ac22b62c551935677000991920b20c2c66a69","tid":2515421,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:52:51.000Z","msg":"有啲似當年共產黨對國民黨個種玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}